{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:18:56.104Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude Code documentation and video breakdown, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Taking Action\""},{"type":"text","text":" is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"second phase of the agentic loop"},{"type":"text","text":" where Claude executes tools to make changes after understanding the problem."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After gathering context and understanding the problem, Claude "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"acts"},{"type":"text","text":" by editing files, running commands, and creating new code. This is where Claude makes actual changes to your project rather than just investigating."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Activities in This Phase"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Action"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Does"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Edit files"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Makes additions (green lines) and removals (red lines) to code"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Run commands"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Executes terminal commands like tests, builds, or scripts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Create new code"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generates new files or functions"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool calls"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each action is a tool call that returns information for the next decision"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The action phase follows a clear cycle:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude reasons"},{"type":"text","text":" about what to do based on gathered context"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude emits tool_use blocks"},{"type":"text","text":" — requests to execute tools (not actual execution)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Your code/client executes the tool"},{"type":"text","text":" — e.g., actually edits the file"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool result is appended"},{"type":"text","text":" as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_result"},{"type":"text","text":" block in the conversation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude sees the result"},{"type":"text","text":" and decides the next step"}]}]}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Model → tool_use request → Client executes → tool_result back → Model reasons again"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It Matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taking Action is critical because:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"It's model-driven, not script-based"},{"type":"text","text":" — Claude makes choices at every step based on what it learned from the previous step"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Real feedback loop"},{"type":"text","text":" — After each action, Claude sees real results (failing test, empty search, 404 error) and adapts"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chains dozens of actions"},{"type":"text","text":" — Claude can chain multiple tool calls together and course-correct along the way"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Separates agent from chatbot"},{"type":"text","text":" — Without tools, Claude only responds with text. With tools, it can actually modify your codebase"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it like a developer actually fixing code: after reading error output and understanding the problem, you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"edit the file"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"run the test"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"see if it passes"},{"type":"text","text":". Claude does this autonomously through tool calls, but the loop is the same."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Taking Action is phase 2 of Claude's 3-phase loop: gather context → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"take action"},{"type":"text","text":" → verify results"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each action is a tool call that returns information feeding the next decision"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model requests tools but never executes them — the application/client executes tools"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Loop continues when "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason: \"tool_use\""},{"type":"text","text":", terminates when "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason: \"end_turn\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verification is an explicit action inside the loop, not an afterthought"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The action phase doesn't guarantee task completion — tools may fail or the task may be impossible, which is why "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"max_turns"},{"type":"text","text":" exists as a safety limit."}]}]}}
